name: MAP OF NFTYTOPIA
description: NFTYtopia is a special island filled with pups who explore and play while they wait to be adopted. . . . Visit NFTY Beach, Pup Plains, Starfall Lake, Wolf Mountains, Howling Caves, Midnight Jungle, Slobber Swamp, Dingo Dunes, Coyote Canyon, Crystal Tundra, Foxen Forest, NFTY City, and Ember Islet. . . . .What treasures will be found within?
